&lt;p&gt;This issue was actually addressed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-8808&quot; title=&quot;Allow @Configuration classes to self-@ComponentScan&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-8808&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-8808&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, and now available in RC2.  Note particularly the resolution comment on that issue to understand the fix and why it doesn&apos;t require a default &lt;tt&gt;excludeFilters&lt;/tt&gt; at all.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
